    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a champ. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily errands and the occasional road trip. It looks great and drives even better\u2014perfect if you're looking for a quality car that's ready to hit the road today. I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, and I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
