    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-maintained, reliable car that has been treated with care. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the passenger-side mirror cap\u2014typical signs of careful road use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in. The upholstery is free of rips or stains, the dashboard is crack-free, and all interior electronics, including the infotainment system and heated seats, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; it starts immediately, idles smoothly, and the transmission provides seamless gear changes. It comes with a complete folder of service records, including a recent brake service and a fresh oil change. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, ensuring you won't need an upgrade anytime soon. This is an honest, solid vehicle that drives as well as it looks.",
      "price": 36500.0,
