    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new-to-you ride? This car has been such a joy to own and is still running like a champ. It\u2019s been well-taken care of and is totally ready for its next adventure! It has a few minor beauty marks from normal use, but it\u2019s honestly in great shape and drives super smooth. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home\u2014feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
